            <thetext>This topic has come up repeatedly over the past few years.  We need to be able to add parameters to the URL even on POST requests, for such things as avoiding caching.  There is a method for adding data to the request, setData(), but it requires that the user build up their data ahead of time rather than allowing the piecemeal addition of one parameter at a time, as is done with setParameter().  Add that ability.</thetext>
